{"declarations":[{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Init/Linter.html#builtin_nolint\"><span class=\"name\">builtin_nolint</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Lean.ParserDescr\">Lean.ParserDescr</a></div></div>","info":{"doc":"`@[builtin_nolint linterName*]` omits the tagged declaration from being checked by\nthe named builtin linters in `lake builtin-lint`. ","docLink":"./Init/Linter.html#builtin_nolint","kind":"def","line":13,"name":"builtin_nolint","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/68218e876d2a38b1985b8590fff244a83c321783/src/Init/Linter.lean#L13-L15"}}],"imports":["Init.Notation"],"instances":[],"name":"Init.Linter"}